Name: Mochi Jump
About the game: Mochi Jump is a simple, fun and addictive challenge of your reactions and reflexes. Control your little mochi, simply click and hold to make them jump. Make sure you time your jumps and judge their heights carefully as you climb moving platforms higher and higher while collecting stars to unlock new mochis and different colours.
